            },
            {
                "paragraph": {
                    "spaceBefore": 20,
                    "string": "<i>Re: Medication Opportunity - ALERT</i>",
                    "text_style": {
                        "parent_style": "BiggerText"
                    }
                }
            },
            {
                "paragraph": {
                    "spaceBefore": 20,
                    "string": "Dear {provider_full_name},",
                    "text_style": {
                        "parent_style": "ParagraphText"
                    }
                }
            },
            {
                "paragraph": {
                    "string": "Blue Cross\u00ae and Blue Shield\u00ae of Vermont is committed to ensuring our members receive seamless and highquality care. Our approach integrates the management of behavioral, pharmacy and physical health care benefits. We have implemented a Provider Outreach Program to collaborate and assist you in providing safe, appropriate, and cost-effective care to patients. As part of this program, drug utilization algorithms based on evidence-based guidelines are utilized to identify any potential medication-related concerns.",
                    "text_style": {
                        "parent_style": "ParagraphText"
                    }
                }
            },
            {
                "paragraph": {
                    "string": "<b>This letter has been generated because we have identified a member-specific opportunity. Please review the information at the top of each page and the corresponding patient list to determine if a change in therapy should be made.</b>",
                    "text_style": {
                        "parent_style": "ParagraphText"
                    }
                }
            },
            {
                "paragraph": {
                    "string": "A clinical pharmacist may contact you to schedule a consultation and explain how the information can be used to support your prescribing decisions and help reduce the risks of adverse effects. You may also request a personal consultation, provide feedback, or request additional data by contacting your dedicated pharmacist at 1-802-491-3297.",
                    "text_style": {
                        "parent_style": "ParagraphText"
                    }
                }
            },
            {
                "paragraph": {
                    "string": "All patients listed in this document have received a prescription with your National Provider Identifier (NPI) number identified as the prescriber. Please be aware that some of these patients may have received a prescription from you at a different site of service, as this mailing is directed to the address primarily associated with your DEA.",
                    "text_style": {
                        "parent_style": "ParagraphText"
                    }
                }
            },
            {
                "paragraph": {
                    "string": "The enclosed information is derived from pharmacy and medical claims data; additional claims paid by cash or other insurance will not be listed. If you receive information you believe to be inaccurate, please contact our tollfree number at 1-802-491-3297 and destroy the information in a confidential manner.",
                    "text_style": {
                        "parent_style": "ParagraphText"
                    }
                }
            },
            {
                "paragraph": {
                    "string": "Sincerely,",
                    "text_style": {
                        "parent_style": "ParagraphText"
                    }
                }
            },
            {
                "image": {
                    "filename": "/images/signature_elizabeth_gilhooly.png",
                    "height": 50,
